desc: This is the initial release of the Clinical Genomics Incubator Implementation Guide for Additional Resources for initial ballot May 2026.
title: Clinical Genomics Incubator Implementation Guide for Additional Resources
introduction: The Clinical Genomics Incubato Implementation Guide for Additional Resources hosts two main genomic resources, i.e., Genomic Study and Molecular Definition resources to be leveraged by Genomics Reporting and Molecular Definition Data Types Implementation Guides.
